& changelog
RECENT CHANGES (2025):

Modernization Phase:
  ✓ Converted all K&R C to ANSI C prototypes
  ✓ Replaced all sprintf/strcpy with safe alternatives
  ✓ Added GoodObject/ValidObject checks throughout
  ✓ Implemented SAFE_MALLOC/SMART_FREE system
  ✓ Replaced gperf with hash table system
  ✓ Merged funcs.c into eval.c
  ✓ Created unified hash system
  ✓ Added DBREF_FMT macro for portability
  ✓ Fixed size_t variable usage
  ✓ Enhanced compiler warning coverage

Features Added:
  ✓ Parser system framework
  ✓ Universe system (experimental)
  ✓ Enhanced channel system
  ✓ Improved mail/board integration
  ✓ Code paste system
  ✓ Comprehensive help system

Bug Fixes:
  ✓ Fixed command dispatch fall-through
  ✓ Fixed channel default validation
  ✓ Fixed pre-login WHO ANSI codes
  ✓ Fixed @poof recycle bin attribute display
  ✓ Fixed numerous buffer overflow vulnerabilities
  ✓ Fixed memory leaks

For detailed commit history, see the source repository.
